Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.41,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:51.28,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs22.5}Not being able to do anything…\NHow powerless I am. How useless I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:47.64,Serifa Std,,0,0,410,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:50.18,Serifa Std,,0,0,410,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.78,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Brother, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.95,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,What is... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.03,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.43,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Is this Armony's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.90,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:14.90,Serifa Std,,0,0,410,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:30.25,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:35.02,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:40.06,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,You might hate me. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:42.86,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Silly Dad, why would I hate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.40,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Enough, don't strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.30,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,You probably didn't realize it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:52.77,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,But I’ve always loved you more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:56.65,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,But I never understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:05.89,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs22.5}What would make you the happiest?\NWhat could I do to give you that happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.16,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,You're so silly, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.06,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Armony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:14.83,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,I always knew all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:21.04,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.67,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.91,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:27.94,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,I am your daughter, right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:30.68,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,You silly one, of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:37.82,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,I see. Then we're both silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:41.29,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Like father, like daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.22,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Armony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.49,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,The light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:49.36,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I won't let you go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.47,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,This is just for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:04.55,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF0FFFF&}I'm sorry, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:09.07,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF0FFFF&}But, you know, I...
